title: PM meets PTI leaders from Mianwali
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jan 31 (APP): The leaders of the Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf from Mianwaliâ€™s NA-95 constituency Monday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan here.
Those who met the prime minister included Ataullah Shadikhel, Ahmed Khan Niazi, Saleem Gul, Jamal Ahsan and Shahid Hameed.
The meeting discussed political matters and those related to the development projects in the constituency.
